---
title: Chicken and Corn Chowder with Green Onions
description: This chowder made for chilly winter nights is calling your name! Chicken and corn make a hearty combo in this big bowl of goodness, while a touch of jalapeños kicks up the flavour. Time to get cozy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chaudree-de-poulet-et-de-mais-51660eb9.jpg
